091F8A44.Line13.6DE47: I’m done for. Your mother told me this trinket would bring good fortune. To think I trusted her.

47AEBA84.Line31.6DE47: She bribed you with it, didn’t she? You weren’t supposed to let her through at all.

5B6CE5A3.Line21.6DE47: The other woman, Vhenard. Where is she?

728D3FDE.Line11.FA726: She begged for her life. Lilith spared her, led her deeper in. Give up, girl. She’s lost.

7B97AD88.Line35.6DE47: Not by me. Not anymore. Prava will know what to do.

916B4ED1.Line5.FA726: A woman. Vigo, it was one of the women you sent.

AF80A08C.Line39.6DE47: There’s nothing left to abandon. (sigh) She's good as dead. I’m sorry, kid.

C55441D5.Line9.FA726: Only she wasn’t human, she was a...a demon, like the statue! Claimed she mothered Sanctuary. It was a damn bloodbath.

E1A33406.Line33.6DE47: But it's not too late. She can still be saved!

F8C38E41.Line23.FA726: Vigo, you must listen. Steel did nothing. Spells, prayers. All useless. Go to Kor Valar. Tell Prava. Raise the army, the Father. Evil itself walks Sanctuary.
